title: Best Jungler of all time?
body:
This is a list of most champs who have seen some reasonable jungling potential. This list may not include all the possible champions who make sense as junglers, but overall I think I included most of the possible junglers. Who do you find has been the most consistent and game changing jungler of all time. I know it depends on meta, but if we were to look at the history of League in its entity, who would you crown as the greatest jungler of all time?
